'''AruMed''' was a biotech company owned by the [[Corporate Sector Authority/Legends|Corporate Sector Authority]] and was based on [[Roonadan]] in the [[Corporate Sector/Legends|Corporate Sector]].

In [[40 ABY/Legends|40 ABY]]. [[Boba Fett/Legends|Boba Fett]] went there in search of the [[Kaminoan/Legends|Kaminoan]] [[Taun We/Legends|Taun We]].

On the [[Planet/Legends|planet]] [[Nyriaan/Legends|Nyriaan]], AruMed administered the settlement [[Arumed]] for the Corporate Sector Authority.<ref name="GOI">''[[Galaxy of Intrigue]]''</ref>

